data.description: Welcome to a home with endless opportunities perched on a large, idyllic tree-covered lot overlooking the beautiful Lake Kiowa golf course! Become a part of this vibrant community by being so close to the club house, lodge, pro-shop & boat ramp. Walk into an open floor plan with two living rooms, one which has a picture window to soak up your stunning views of the golf course and a screened-in porch perfect for relaxing. Three bedrooms offer plenty of room to make this home your own. The garage has room to park two cars and a golf cart, plenty of room for storage & a shed in the backyard. With some basic updating this home is sure to be your new oasis especially with the incredible treed huge lot. Lake Kiowa is a gated community with 24-hour security and residents enjoy unlimited golf on a rated course! The 635 acre lake is large enough for water skiing, boating and fishing! Tennis courts are also located within the community. Great opportunity w home priced according to updating need.
